            "**enabled**: Is syslog enabled?",
            "**host**: Syslog server (IP or FQDN)",
            "**logIpEnabled**: Determines whether user’s IP address is logged.",
            "**port**: Syslog server port",
            "**protocol**: Protocol to connect to syslog server"
